author: JerryRigEverything
description:
Here in Utah it gets cold QUICK! This week Cambry and I are getting our garden ready for winter - and staying warm in our new @Carhartt gear. Cambry is wearing a new bomber jacket, and I'm wearing a sherpa lined utility jacket from Carhartt’s Reworked program. Living multiple lives is the definition of durable! You can find every gift you want to give this year at Carhartt.com

Get your own Carhartt Gear HERE: https://www.carhartt.com/c/zack-nelson
